Bahrain posts 38 mln dinar trade surplus in Q1 97 . Bahrain on Wednesday reported a 38 million dinar ( $ 100 . 8 million ) foreign trade surplus in the first quarter of 1997 after posting a 48 . 2 million dinar surplus in the fourth quarter of 1996 , the Bahrain Monetary Agency said . BAHRAIN TRADE ( million Bahraini dinars ) Q1 97 Q4 96 Q3 96 Q2 96 Q1 96Total exports 419 . 40 471 . 00 421 . 60 418 . 80 419 . 10 oil 283 . 20 335 . 60 277 . 70 284 . 40 289 . 40 non - oil * 136 . 20 135 . 40 143 . 90 134 . 40 129 . 70Total imports 381 . 40 422 . 80 362 . 70 371 . 30 382 . 00 oil 153 . 50 189 . 60 149 . 50 164 . 70 167 . 00 non - oil * 227 . 90 233 . 20 213 . 20 206 . 60 215 . 00Trade balance + 38 . 0 + 48 . 2 + 58 . 9 + 47 . 5 + 37 . 1 * 1997 provisional . - - Bahrain newsroon 973 - 524424 . 
